| Vercel | `https://panda.tail7af24.ts.net/webhooks/vercel` | `https://joels-mac-studio.tail7af24.ts.net:10000/webhooks/vercel` | Maybe API/dashboard; if recreated, update `vercel_webhook_secret` |
| GitHub | `https://panda.tail7af24.ts.net/webhooks/github` | `https://joels-mac-studio.tail7af24.ts.net:10000/webhooks/github` | API or dashboard |
| Mux | `https://panda.tail7af24.ts.net/webhooks/mux` | `https://joels-mac-studio.tail7af24.ts.net:10000/webhooks/mux` | API/dashboard |
| Joelclaw internal | `https://panda.tail7af24.ts.net/webhooks/joelclaw` | `https://joels-mac-studio.tail7af24.ts.net:10000/webhooks/joelclaw` | Repo/env config if used externally |
